Name: The Director's Disorder: Pilot Episode
About the game: In The Director’s Disorder : Pilot Episode , you’ll play the part of Coal Westwood, retired actor, as you attempt to survive the whims of a deadly killer. To live through the night, Coal will need to avoid antagonizing the Director by following the script or risk his wrath. This is the role of a lifetime. Features: - Fully Voiced Dialogue - Striking Visuals - Immersive Sound Design - Multiple Endings Short Horror Experience
